  "title": "Predicate Respects an Equivalence",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $P$ be a predicate on $A$. The predicate $P$ \\emph{respects} $\\sim$ if\n\\[\n\\forall a,a'\\in A,\\,\na\\sim a'\\Longrightarrow \\bigl(P(a)\\Longleftrightarrow P(a')\\bigr).\n\\]",
